{
  "stem": "8892.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And by that time, of course, my sister gets home all right, and they are not in Liszka yet.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler is not in Liszka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody knows.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She goes home and tells them what's going on, and my father finds out that she left me at the station.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I am sure she got hell, but I did, I came home with all the kids who are commuting back to Liszka-- 12 o'clock-- and I was the only Jewish kid.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, they didn't say nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They didn't harm me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was, of course, by that time glad to be home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My father was at the gate waiting for me, because they knew the last train was coming out of [INAUDIBLE] at 11:30 or so.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we were, you know, like 12 o'clock getting home and walk home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I think he was ready to kill me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He hugged me, then slapped me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember getting two slaps on my face and my mother crying and hugging me that I finally safe.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And that's when I know my whole life was turned upside down.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Then I knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, of course, about few days later, the Germans arrive in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the first thing, you know, they go at the-- what do we call it-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] oh, come on.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I can't even think of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They go with a loud speaker, the gendarme, which is a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That was the Hungarian police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They come out to the center of the town with their loud speaker.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "No Jews allowed to step out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Jew's curfew not to walk out of the house, and if they do, they are allowed out from 10 to five.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And they must wear a yellow star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is our town.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
